  "text": "This requirement is necessary to keep the members of a group informed on the group activity and to timely collaborate with other members. Awareness can take various forms such as availability awareness (availability of resources, availability of members, ...), context awareness (where the actions/changes took place), group process awareness (changes with regard to project workflow), etc. [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] . Implementation of these awareness forms enables a timely and effective collaboration and coordination of online groups.",
